  <brief_title>The Effect of Honey on Xerostomia and Oral Mucositis</brief_title>
  <acronym>AC-H</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Control Trial for the Effect of Honey on Radiotherapy Induced Xerostomia and Oral Mucositis in Patients With Head and Neck Cancers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
